README:
Wistar rats (mixed sex) were prepared according to: 
Stenroos P, Paasonen J, Salo RA, et al. Awake Rat Brain Functional Magnetic Resonance Imaging Using Standard Radio Frequency Coils and a 3D Printed Restraint Kit. Front Neurosci. 2018;12:548. Published 2018 Aug 20. doi:10.3389/fnins.2018.00548

Data acquisition in the Nijmegen site for the MultiRat project, in collabration with Amsterdam. 

The raw BIDS data was created using BIDScoin 3.6.3
All provenance information and settings can be found in ./code/bidscoin
For more information see: https://github.com/Donders-Institute/bidscoin
